{"content": "<p>Sometimes you need to see someone else do it first before it makes sense with NFTs, and that's why we've built the <a href=\"http://www.digitalartisteconomy.com/skillsportal\">MintFace Skills Portal</a> for artists and collectors.</p><p>Each irresistibly concise video levels up your skills with NFTs. We cover the easy stuff like <a href=\"http://fast.wistia.com/embed/channel/7lpdwhymbc?wchannelid=7lpdwhymbc&amp;wmediaid=s9sg0yx7xu\">how to transfer eth</a> and NFTs... right through to the hard stuff like <a href=\"http://fast.wistia.com/embed/channel/7lpdwhymbc?wchannelid=7lpdwhymbc&amp;wmediaid=5yizn8ggaz\">how to set up a gnosis wallet</a>.</p><p>🍒 New videos get added every 2 weeks in 2022 so if there's a topic you'd like covered, please let <a href=\"https://twitter.com/mintfaced\">@mintfaced</a> know on Twitter or by reply email.</p><p>If you prefer to learn together with artists like you, <a href=\"http://digitalartisteconomy.com\">join the NFT Digital Artist Economy workshop</a> where by the end you'll know a whole lot more about launching your digital art collection. Applications are <a href=\"http://digitalartisteconomy.com\">now open</a>.</p><h2 id=\"artists\">Artists</h2><figure class=\"kg-card kg-image-card\"><a href=\"https://mintface.wistia.com/embed/channel/7lpdwhymbc\"><img src=\"https://digital-artist-economy.ghost.io/content/images/2025/01/Screen-Shot-2022-01-12-at-5.43.17-PM-1200x289.png\" class=\"kg-image\" alt loading=\"lazy\" width=\"2000\" height=\"481\" srcset=\"https://digital-artist-economy.ghost.io/content/images/2025/01/1_Screen-Shot-2022-01-12-at-5.43.17-PM.png 600w, https://digital-artist-economy.ghost.io/content/images/2025/01/2_Screen-Shot-2022-01-12-at-5.43.17-PM.png 1000w, https://digital-artist-economy.ghost.io/content/images/2025/01/3_Screen-Shot-2022-01-12-at-5.43.17-PM-1200x289.png 1600w, https://digital-artist-economy.ghost.io/content/images/2025/01/4_Screen-Shot-2022-01-12-at-5.43.17-PM-1200x289.png 2400w\" sizes=\"(min-width: 720px) 720px\"></a></figure><h2 id=\"technical\">Technical </h2><figure class=\"kg-card kg-image-card\"><a href=\"https://mintface.wistia.com/embed/channel/7lpdwhymbc\"><img src=\"https://digital-artist-economy.ghost.io/content/images/2025/01/Screen-Shot-2022-01-12-at-5.43.53-PM-1200x260.png\" class=\"kg-image\" alt loading=\"lazy\" width=\"2000\" height=\"433\" srcset=\"https://digital-artist-economy.ghost.io/content/images/2025/01/1_Screen-Shot-2022-01-12-at-5.43.53-PM.png 600w, https://digital-artist-economy.ghost.io/content/images/2025/01/2_Screen-Shot-2022-01-12-at-5.43.53-PM.png 1000w, https://digital-artist-economy.ghost.io/content/images/2025/01/3_Screen-Shot-2022-01-12-at-5.43.53-PM-1200x260.png 1600w, https://digital-artist-economy.ghost.io/content/images/2025/01/4_Screen-Shot-2022-01-12-at-5.43.53-PM-1200x260.png 2400w\" sizes=\"(min-width: 720px) 720px\"></a></figure><h2 id=\"collectors\">Collectors</h2><figure class=\"kg-card kg-image-card\"><a href=\"https://mintface.wistia.com/embed/channel/7lpdwhymbc\"><img src=\"https://digital-artist-economy.ghost.io/content/images/2025/01/Screen-Shot-2022-01-12-at-5.42.34-PM-1200x268.png\" class=\"kg-image\" alt loading=\"lazy\" width=\"2000\" height=\"446\" srcset=\"https://digital-artist-economy.ghost.io/content/images/2025/01/1_Screen-Shot-2022-01-12-at-5.42.34-PM.png 600w, https://digital-artist-economy.ghost.io/content/images/2025/01/2_Screen-Shot-2022-01-12-at-5.42.34-PM.png 1000w, https://digital-artist-economy.ghost.io/content/images/2025/01/3_Screen-Shot-2022-01-12-at-5.42.34-PM-1200x268.png 1600w, https://digital-artist-economy.ghost.io/content/images/2025/01/4_Screen-Shot-2022-01-12-at-5.42.34-PM-1200x268.png 2400w\" sizes=\"(min-width: 720px) 720px\"></a></figure><h2 id=\"security\">Security </h2><figure class=\"kg-card kg-image-card kg-card-hascaption\"><a href=\"https://mintface.wistia.com/embed/channel/7lpdwhymbc\"><img src=\"https://digital-artist-economy.ghost.io/content/images/2025/01/Screen-Shot-2022-01-12-at-5.44.38-PM-1200x271.png\" class=\"kg-image\" alt loading=\"lazy\" width=\"2000\" height=\"452\" srcset=\"https://digital-artist-economy.ghost.io/content/images/2025/01/1_Screen-Shot-2022-01-12-at-5.44.38-PM.png 600w, https://digital-artist-economy.ghost.io/content/images/2025/01/2_Screen-Shot-2022-01-12-at-5.44.38-PM.png 1000w, https://digital-artist-economy.ghost.io/content/images/2025/01/3_Screen-Shot-2022-01-12-at-5.44.38-PM-1200x271.png 1600w, https://digital-artist-economy.ghost.io/content/images/2025/01/4_Screen-Shot-2022-01-12-at-5.44.38-PM-1200x271.png 2400w\" sizes=\"(min-width: 720px) 720px\"></a><figcaption>`</figcaption></figure><p>How to Transfer An Artwork is one I get asked ALOT! Please share this on Twitter :)</p><figure class=\"kg-card kg-embed-card\"><blockquote class=\"twitter-tweet\"><p lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\">🍒How To Transfer An Artwork<br /><br />feat. <a href=\"https://twitter.com/monstersofmind?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">@monstersofmind</a> <br /><br />RT <a href=\"https://t.co/tUT8JrjjWf\">pic.twitter.com/tUT8JrjjWf</a></p>&mdash; mintface.eth (@mintfaced) <a href=\"https://twitter.com/mintfaced/status/1481110113805271045?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">January 12, 2022</a></blockquote><script async src=\"https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js\" charset=\"utf-8\"></script></figure><p></p><hr /><p>Receive new artist features by email.</p><div class=\"kg-card kg-button-card kg-align-left\"><a href=\"https://digital-artist-economy.ghost.io/#/portal/signup\" class=\"kg-btn kg-btn-accent\">Subscribe to MintFace</a></div><div class=\"kg-card kg-callout-card kg-callout-card-pink\"><div class=\"kg-callout-emoji\">💡</div><div class=\"kg-callout-text\"><strong>Artists. Join the next <a href=\"https://maven.com/mintface/nft-digital-artist-economy\">Digital Artist Economy Accelerator</a> </strong>and launch your NFT collection with confidence on your own smart contract.</div></div><div class=\"kg-card kg-callout-card kg-callout-card-purple\"><div class=\"kg-callout-emoji\">💡</div><div class=\"kg-callout-text\"><strong>Collectors. </strong><a href=\"https://digital-artist-economy.ghost.io/#/portal/signup\">Subscribe to MintFace Premium</a> for $USD9 per month. MintFace surfaces great artists and artworks so you don't have to.</div></div>"}